                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180218-88-off464 t18180218-88-crimeloc467"></join>. On the 12th of January, the coat hung at the door for sale.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180218-88-person557">
                  JOHN 
                  HARRISON
               <interp inst="t18180218-88-person557" type="surname" value="HARRISON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180218-88-person557" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180218-88-person557" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was in Chumley's shop, and saw the prisoner come to the door, take the coat down, and run away with it - I pursued - He fell down about six yards from the door. I came up and took him with it.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I was in great distress.</p>
